oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall sitting on a wooden fence
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of Lieutenant Colonel J.Y. Kinsall sitting on a wooden fence at Happy Valley-Goose Bay in Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada.

From 1947-1948, Kinsall served as a Director of Personnel and Administrative Services while stationed at the Canadian Forces Base Goose Bay at Happy Valley-Goose Bay in Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada.
